---
title: Kiwi-Spiced Beef Rissoles & Mint Sauce with Roasted Veggies & Almonds
description: These simple beef rissoles are packed with flavour, using our Kiwi spice blend! They’re the perfect little parcels of joy, to be savoured with your favourite roast veg and a drizzle of mint sauce.
